rtical-align:baseline;line-height:24px;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">小肥羊在37 Avenue上，著名的法拉盛大停车场旁边。停车非常方便。附近还有功夫奶茶店，麻辣烫和英式下午茶的好地方玫瑰花园(Rose Garden)。我们到达小肥羊的时候时光尚早，于是去店里约了个号，在旁边的Skyblue KTV唱了两个小时的歌，才又饥肠辘辘的转战火锅店。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:24px;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">我们点了最常见的鸳鸯火锅，肥羊，肥牛，菌类拼盘，豆腐拼盘，蔬菜拼盘，花枝丸等等。鸳鸯火锅的白汤是小肥羊著名的，我们在煮上火锅之前就迫不及待的每人喝上了了一大碗。鲜美的舌头都要掉了～ 味道和国内的真差不多。特别解馋。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:24px;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">蔬菜拼盘的份量非常的大。如果吃的人不是特别多，点了一份蔬菜拼盘之后就不需要别的单点蔬菜了。我最喜欢里面的西洋菜和南瓜了。西红柿放在清汤里也很鲜美。</p>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_427\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:4px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;max-width:100%;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:24px;width:310px;\"><img src=\"http://nyctaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/%E8%94%AC%E8%8F%9C%E6%8B%BC%E7%9B%98-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"小肥羊\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-427\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;max-width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 1px 4px;\" height=\"225\" width=\"300\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:0.857142857rem;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:2;font-style:italic;color:#757575;\">蔬菜拼盘</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:24px;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n鱼滑是一定要极力推荐，入口鲜滑有韧劲，特别抢手，是大家的最爱！</p>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_428\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:4px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;max-width:100%;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:24px;width:310px;\"><img src=\"http://nyctaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/%E9%B1%BC%E6%BB%91-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"小肥羊\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-428\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;max-width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 1px 4px;\" height=\"225\" width=\"300\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:0.857142857rem;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:2;font-style:italic;color:#757575;\">鱼滑</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:24px;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_429\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:4px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;max-width:100%;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:24px;width:310px;\"><img src=\"http://nyctaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/%E9%B1%BC%E9%A5%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E8%B1%86%E8%85%90%E5%92%8C%E8%8A%B1%E6%9E%9D%E4%B8%B8-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"小肥羊\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-429\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;max-width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 1px 4px;\" height=\"225\" width=\"300\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:0.857142857rem;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:2;font-style:italic;color:#757575;\">鱼饺，鱼豆腐和花枝丸</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:24px;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n另外值得一提的是他们的烤羊肉串。羊肉味很足，辣椒孜然都够味。不过小心不要一下吃太多，不然就吃不下火锅咯～</p>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_424\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:4px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;max-width:100%;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:24px;width:310px;\"><img src=\"http://nyctaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/%E7%BE%8A%E8%82%89%E4%B8%B2-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"羊肉串\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-424\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;max-width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 1px 4px;\" height=\"225\" width=\"300\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;font-size:0.857142857rem;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:2;font-style:italic;color:#757575;\">羊肉串</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:24px;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.714285714rem;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:24px;color:#444444;font-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">小肥羊的地址是136-59 37th Ave, Flushing, Queens, NY。店里接受订座，还有包间。包间的话最低消费200美金，同时自动收18%的服务费。坐地铁前往的话建议坐7号线到Flushing Main Street下，然后往北走两三个街区就到了。</p>','11111111111111111111111111111111',NULL,NULL,NULL,'','coupon','none','N','N','goods','100','1442505600','1431187200','1442505600','1431719183','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N;','15','58','4.0','N','N','','0','92','','','周一到周五，下午2:00---7:00','美味火锅尽在小肥羊火锅店，您和朋友的聚会第一选择','3','8');
